snippet.title: Rivals 2 Maypul Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Maypul joins the cast in Rivals 2 as the latest character in our 2024 launch roster! The Sylvan Watcher returns with her trusty plant companion Lily, along with 2 new flora friends Terry and Poppy. Revealed live on the #evo2023  main stage. Learn more and show your support for the game at https://rivals2.com/wishlist
#rivalsofaether #rivals2 #indiegame
